items.title: Paramedic and police officer seriously hurt while attending crash
items.description: Three men are arrested after a paramedic and an officer attending an earlier crash were seriously hurt.

items.title: Man dies after tree falls onto caravan during Storm Goretti
items.description: Police say a man in his 50s died in the incident in Helston during Storm Goretti.

items.title: TV psychologist on inspiring Prince Naseem film
items.description: A new movie starring Pierce Brosnan reveals the bond between Prince Naseem Hamed and his trainer.

items.title: Non-league Macclesfield stun FA Cup holders Crystal Palace
items.description: Sixth-tier Macclesfield FC beat reigning champions Crystal Palace. With 117 places between the teams, it's the biggest upset in FA Cup history.

items.title: Video emerges of Minneapolis shooting filmed by ICE agent who opened fire
items.description: The clip shows the moments before gunfire rang out on a Minneapolis street.
